metadata.name: Blood Thirst in the Big Apple #1
metadata.description:
Once upon a time, in the bustling city of New York, there lived a vampire named Alexander. He had lived for centuries, and had seen the city change and grow over the years. He often roamed the dark alleys and underground subway tunnels at night, in search of his next meal.
